import { Component } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-tabels', templateUrl: './tabels.component.html', styleUrls: ['./tabels.component.scss'] }) export class TabelsComponent { }
SEO
focus keyphrase
title maximum 397pixels
meta description minimum 93 letters maximum 118
keyphrase in title
keyphrase in meta description
keyphrase in introduction
keyphrase in subheadings Must in H1, Recomended in H2 and H3

READABILITY
plagiarism
grammer
spellings
words count minimum 300 words
consecutive sentences not a single one

paragraph length maximum 150 words
passive voice maximum 10% of the text
subheading distribution
transition words minimum 15% 25% sentences
word complexity maximum 10% of the text
